Inserts a new Meeting record in the database and returns a MediaIndex object representing this record.

Parameters:
DBConnection - dbcon com.compendium.core.db.management.DBConnection, the DBConnection object to access the database with.
sMeetingID, - the id of this meeting.
sMeetingMapID, - the id of the main parent meeting map
sMeetingName, - the name the meeting is known as in Compendium.
dMeetingDate, - the date of the meeting.
nStatus, - the status of this meeting. Either ICoreConstants.STATUS_PREPARED or ICoreConstants.STATUS_RECORDED
Returns:
boolean, true if it was successful, else false.
